OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FThat milestone anniversary is being
OL,7,Fcited as the reason why King Charles
OL,8,Fis visiting the US now.
OL,10,FPreparations for the trip have
OL,11,Freportedly taken 40 hours of work per
OL,12,Fminute of the monarch's trip.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
