OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FEvery detail, no matter how small, has
OL,7,Fbeen poured over, checked, altered and
OL,8,Fchecked again; from the choice of
OL,9,Fsparkling wine at the Embassy Garden
OL,10,FParty (British, of course) to the last
OL,11,Fword of both speeches the King will
OL,12,Fgive to Congress and at a state
OL,13,Fbanquet inside the East Room of the
OL,14,FWhite House, nothing is being left to
OL,15,Fchance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
