OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FSenior British officials have pointed
OL,7,Fout to the White House that while the
OL,8,FBritish Monarch is the Head of State,
OL,9,Fhe "doesn't do politics" and is hoping
OL,10,FDonald Trump's famous verbal weave
OL,11,Fdoesn't stray into areas which will
OL,12,Fcause diplomatic ripples.
OL,14,FThere is an acceptance that the high-
OL,15,Fprofile rift between Sir Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fand Donald Trump has been challenging,
OL,17,Fbut sources stress that behind-the-
OL,18,Fscenes cooperation between the two
OL,19,Fcountries, when it comes to defence,
OL,20,Fintelligence, trade and investment,
OL,21,Fhas continued to work well.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
