OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FThis will be Charles' 20th visit to
OL,7,Fthe United States, but his first as
OL,8,FKing.
OL,10,FHis schedule is packed, including a
OL,11,FRoyal Garden party at the Embassy,
OL,12,Fceremonial events in Washington,
OL,13,Ffollowed by a trip to Virginia, a
OL,14,Fvisit to New York and then a stop in
OL,15,FBermuda on the way home.
OL,17,FIt will not include meeting survivors
OL,18,Fof the disgraced paedophile Jeffrey
OL,19,FEpstein, a decision taken "on legal
OL,20,Fadvice", because of the requirement
OL,21,Fnot to affect pending court cases.
OL,26,@{D@[OU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
