OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777057867
OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FInstead, the theme will be the "arc of
OL,7,Fhistory" between the two nations, a
OL,8,Fbond bigger than the current
OL,9,Fincumbents of either Head of State. It
OL,10,Fhas endured political challenges over
OL,11,Fthe years.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FA symbol of that alliance will be the
OL,19,Fgifts exchanged at the White House
OL,20,Fbetween the King and the President.
OL,26,@nD@`OUoD@HO]
