OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FThe details of that will be released
OL,7,Fby the Palace in the coming days.
OL,9,FThere will be no chance, we are told,
OL,10,Ffor reporters to ask questions when
OL,11,Fthe King and President are together.
OL,13,FThe greatest moment of jeopardy is
OL,14,FPresident Trump saying something
OL,15,Funexpected in his Majesty's presence
OL,16,Fand causing a diplomatic incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
