OL,3,CFinal preparations: Choreographing the
OL,4,CKing's visit to the US
OL,6,FSo instead, this will be an exercise
OL,7,Fakin to carrying a crystal vase across
OL,8,Fa polished floor in socks - one small
OL,9,Fstep at a time, praying for no slip-
OL,10,Fups.
OL,12,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,13,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,14,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,15,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
